Kin To Each Other

Bringing The World To Its Knees

With Their Unified Power
Their Mounts Not Forsaken
The Mad God's Return

So Listen To Me

They Are Axieros the Mother

Kersa and Kersos
Sister and Brother.

Visionaries prosper, gaining foresight into their endeavours.
If ones endeavour is to control through power, then one must see the
advantage of Might.
The Sacred Flames understand this, using the Sword as their Symbol, to carry their Vision forwards.
If one is to see, then one must grasp the sword by it's Hilt, for only then will the True Visionary have the Might to Proceed.

There are many Bonds that can be made between souls that reside on different realms from each other.
One such bond, is that of The Sacred Flames and their Dragon Mounts.
In times gone past, this pairing reigned terror across the skies.
Like the Phoenix rising from the ashes, their immortality is everlasting, for only when both are slain, will they truly be laid to rest.
